	<h3>Related Documents</h3>      
	<ul>
	
	<li><a href="/en/consumer_affairs/consumer_protection/consumer_rights/consumers_and_the_law_in_ireland.html">Your rights as a consumer in Ireland</a><br>In Ireland, the rights of consumers are protected by Irish and EU laws.  Consumer legislation is described here along with information about deposits and redress mechanisms.</li>
	
	<li><a href="/en/consumer_affairs/consumer_protection/consumer_rights/consumer_advertising.html">Consumer advertising</a><br>Consumers in Ireland and the EU are protected from false or misleading advertising.  Find out what the rules are governing advertisers and what to do if you have been deceived by an advert.</li>
	
	<li><a href="/en/consumer_affairs/consumer_protection/consumer_rights/consumer_rights_and_cross_border_shopping_in_the_european_union.html">Consumer rights in the European Union</a><br>All consumers purchasing goods in the EU are entitled to some basic rights. Find out about your rights if you buy goods from or in another EU Member State.</li>
	
